<div class="status-header">
    <div class="tag">Quote Received</div>
    <h1>New Quote for {{rfqId}}</h1>
    <p>A seller has submitted a new quote for your open RFQ. Review the pricing and terms below.</p>
</div>

<div class="highlight-box">
    <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Quote Summary</div>
        <div class="info-value" style="font-size: 24px; color: #2563eb;">₹{{landedPrice}} / MT</div>
        <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #64748b;">Landed Rate for {{quantity}} MT</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="divider"></div>
    
    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
        <tr>
            <td width="50%" style="padding-right: 10px;">
                <div class="info-label">Seller</div>
                <div class="info-value">{{sellerName}}</div>
            </td>
            <td width="50%">
                <div class="info-label">Lead Time</div>
                <div class="info-value">{{leadDays}} Days</div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>

<div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
    <a href="{{rfqUrl}}" class="btn">Compare & Accept Quote</a>
</div>

<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-size: 13px; color: #64748b; text-align: center; font-style: italic;">
    Tip: Accepting a quote early ensures better availability of material and logistics slots.
</p>
